product_name: Keen Sterling City MJ Shoes - Women's - 2013 Closeout
long_description: Keen Sterling City Mary Jane Shoes combine sleek leather uppers with rugged outsoles, letting you transition seamlessly from your office to an evening walk around the lake or dog park. Full-grain leather uppers offer flexible comfort and durability; patented toe bumpers protect feet from abrasion. Breathable synthetic mesh linings wick moisture away from skin for lasting comfort. Removable polyurethane and memory foam footbeds plus polyurethane midsoles provide excellent cushioning and support for long days on your feet. Nonmarking rubber outsoles deliver reliable traction on a variety of surfaces. Closeout.
